            "tol": 0.01,
            "explain": "The map $\\theta \\mapsto 2\\sqrt{p}\\cos\\theta$ is a bijection $[0,\\pi] \\to [-2\\sqrt{p}, 2\\sqrt{p}]$, so $\\theta_p \\in [0,\\pi]$, of length $\\pi$."
